<h1>About swissbib</h1>
<h2>Search centrally - order locally</h2>
<p>Search centrally in the libraries of all Swiss universities, universities for applied science, federal research
    stations, the Swiss national library, and many more.</p>
<p>swissbib can be used for finding media and informing yourself about the holding libraries. For ordering the book you
    have to switch to the local library.</p>

<h2>What does swissbib contain?</h2>
<p>swissbib lets you search in 19.8 million documents from <a href="../libraries/index.html"><b>823 libraries, media
            centers and archives</b></a> from all parts of the country within one user interface.</p>
<p>This covers books, journals, theses, ebooks, digitized materials, movies (from VHS to Bluray), music (from sheets,
    partitions and LPs to DVDs) audiobooks, photos, learning materials and many more...</p>

