<h2>project swissbib</h2>
<p>swissbib is a cooperative project of the Swiss university libraries, the Swiss national library under the lead of the
    Universitätsbibliothek Basel and is a part of the infrastructure project &raquo;e-lib.ch - Swiss electronic library&laquo;.
    From 2008 to 2013 it is funded by SUC - Swiss University Conference.</p>